Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:16.82,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.29,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.29,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:27.63,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.55,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:36.47,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:42.27,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:48.19,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.86,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:55.36,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.08,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.87,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:06.75,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.59,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:18.85,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.93,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.73,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
