Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't let myself get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've already been rejected once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.59,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Do you have the usual, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.91,Main Dialog,Woman,0,0,0,,There you are, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.79,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're looking beautiful as always, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.67,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.97,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'll take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:36.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're in shock over the news that Yurika eloped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.43,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's all over the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:44.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you tell him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.89,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, Kawabuchi? I told him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.81,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,I don't think he's in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to hear anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How must he feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.33,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,Ah, that's the one that won the \NPrefectural Governor's Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.66,Main Dialog,Boy B,0,0,0,,We'd better take it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.20,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,You take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.13,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,There's no way the school will display
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.20,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,a painting by a student who's involved in a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.07,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,We were told to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And what's going to happen to it after you take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.68,Main Dialog,Boy B,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This painting is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:39.49,Main Dialog,Boy B,0,0,0,,What's she to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.24,Main Dialog,Boy A,0,0,0,,Had eyes for her, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.79,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Let it go, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Sorry. You can take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't you care what happens to that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Your stupidity must be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:10.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:15.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Seriously, how stupid are you gonna be for somebody else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:16.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait, so what about the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, I already said my goodbye to it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Have you gotten a present \Nfrom someone recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Like something that was knitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:48.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I knitted Sentaro a sweater and used \Nthe leftover yarn to make the mittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:52.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's cruel, but it figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,This. It's called Lily-yarn or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachiko gave it to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Nope. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:05.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,But what am I supposed \Nto do with this string?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing? You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Now you're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.01,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:34.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,U-Um, these are really warm. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ow! Damn it! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Nope, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:52.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we'll be \Nchanging classes again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess third-years are split up \Naccording to their grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so you probably won't be in \Nthe same class as Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Goin' for college entrance exams, right, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm planning on going to college too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about becoming \Nan elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,So you're gonna be a teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:20.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,A long time ago, you said you wanted \Nto have a bakery or cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:26.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Come on, don't you remember? \NYou were a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,That's why you wanted an entire shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, where do you want to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, I... haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,As for me, never mind about college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I might not even make it to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, everything depends on the next make-up exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Start with these basic problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll make you some flash cards in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm just not cut out for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if you fail this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll just quit school an' get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You must be jo—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.64,apollon 2nd,Sen,0,0,0,,It ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,When I think about my family,\NI can't afford to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you flunk this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm tired. I need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait! You're in the middle of these questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If you're going to rest, it'll have to wait till you're done with these problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't! My head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.53,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,B-Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You look really happy when you're surrounded by the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I bet you're going to have \Na big family of your own
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,and have lots of kids around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It'll be a warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.48,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Chi'ko wet herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.48,apollon 2nd,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wet herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.31,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Yay, Chi'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,The bath's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:48.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My ma will dry your pants,\Nso relax till they're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is an unusual setup for a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're out of soap, right? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Sen's family's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Our families share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:32.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... I wish I had given you those mittens earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's almost spring, so you won't \Nneed to use them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:46.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Since you knitted them, I'd like to wear them all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Drops often fall in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sentaro lets out a yelp once in a while himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:03.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,So, why did you give me those mittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why me and not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:20.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I mean, if you've liked him all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! How about havin' dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Your pants aren't dry yet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait, your hair's soakin' wet!\NYou'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But I can't get the idea out of my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,that she probably still has feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Sen, how did the make-up exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.25,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, you passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:29.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.37,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I gotta thank 'im proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen him around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,The day before yesterday, he \Npassed out in class with a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,so he's restin' up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Nope, Ritsuko didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,"Someday My Prince Will Come"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,N-No! That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Look, isn't his house huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,All right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Thank him for me for helpin' me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why? Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.41,Main Dialog,Aunt,0,0,0,,Kaoru, one of your classmates \Nhas come to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hi, Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, is your fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Eat them if you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you go out of your way to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:21.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, no. I didn't buy these. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:29.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, he came here with you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I saw you two out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He should've come in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Never mind. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:47.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You two have been together since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,There's no way I could be a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Unlike me, he's strong and built.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's so handsome that he even takes my breath away once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're better off with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:05.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Stop it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I know what you're saying, \Nso don't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:27.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, don't you like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:33.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,you just don't have any confidence, \Nso you're trying to keep your distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:38.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You told me to have confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.27,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Those words have saved me a number of times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But if it looks like you don't have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I have a feeling I'll lose mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:05.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What I've wished for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.13,Main Dialog,Mariko,0,0,0,,Oh, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.14,Main Dialog,Mariko,0,0,0,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet something happened between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:30.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't come here! I'll go over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:50.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, let me tell you how I feel\Nabout you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you, Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.68,apollon 2nd,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,K-Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:05.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,P-Please! Your relatives can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:16.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not muscular, and maybe I'm \Nnot as manly as I should be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:21.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but when it comes to my feelings for you, I'm second to no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You might catch my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Hey! You're burning up! And you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.19,Main Dialog,Mariko,0,0,0,,That was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.86,apollon 2nd,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:00.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's already summer, and I haven't made any more progress with Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I was so bold when I had that fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me when \Nmy temperature is normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I want to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Touch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How long have you been in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Both of you! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,"The Olympus Has Thrown Down the Gauntlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:27.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,"The Olympus is going to win at this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:30.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru to Seiji,0,0,0,,It seems there are still some \Nold-fashioned jazz musicians around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.57,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,but this is the era of rock n' roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,They were handing this \Nout all over the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't take this sitting down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You two are gonna perform in the festival, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:54.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,We start with "Moanin'" to fire up \Nthe people that saw us last year
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,an' trick 'em into thinking we're \Ngonna do the same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But then we move into some other \Nsongs that we want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I was thinkin' the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,All right, let's choose our next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Starting today, we'd better \Npractice every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:11.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.28,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:18.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.24,apollon 2nd,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.70,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Look, I got surprising news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.54,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Dad says he's comin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.87,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,This way, the whole family can live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.60,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I can't say that I'm actually scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:56.57,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,See, our Dad, who was working far \Naway, is coming home tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:01.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, I'm one of those that ain't got a place in the house too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.37,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.12,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, you're back late, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What's Richie doin' here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I see. Unlike Kota and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,you remember how scary Dad \Nwas when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,But don't worry, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:36.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ma told me that he worked really \Nhard an' quit drinkin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.24,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. You got nothin' \Nto worry about, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Now how about comin' inside \Nan' we can prepare together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:45.66,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:54.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for lookin' after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:58.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're the one I'm worried about, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:09.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Dope! What are you lookin' so serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What? I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.45,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:22.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you coming to practice tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:33.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. After all, playin' with \Nyou is the most fun I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.72,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, what are you writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Hm... Nah, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,It's not comin' out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ah, well. Let's get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, I'm sorry for lyin' to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:10.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I was looking forward to the\Nfestival too. I wanted to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Be good to Ri'ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Take care.
